Installation in a central location:

   $ python setup.py install

Installation in your home directory:

   $ python setup.py install --prefix=$HOME/pbsclusterviz

Then you need to set your PYTHONPATH environment variable so:

   export PYTHONPATH=$HOME/pbsclusterviz/lib

and extend your PATH so:

   export PATH=$PATH:$HOME/pbsclusterviz/scripts-2.5


Dependencies:
   python 2.5, Visualisation Toolkit (python-vtk), Python XML libraries (python-xml)
